          public String handle() {
              return "error";
          }
      }

Interceptors :Similar to filters but Spring-specific
    Used for:
            Logging
            Authentication
            Pre/Post processing
            public class MyInterceptor implements HandlerInterceptor {
                public boolean preHandle(...) {}
            }

 Filters vs Interceptors:
    Feature	                        Filter	  Interceptor
    Type	                          Servlet	  Spring
    Runs before DispatcherServlet	  ✅	      ❌
    Access to Spring Beans	        ❌	      ✅
    
Configuration Types:
    🔹 XML (Old) - <bean class="DispatcherServlet"/>
    🔹 Java Config
          @Configuration
          @EnableWebMvc
    🔹 Spring Boot (Auto) - No config needed
Real-Time Use Cases:
